Avl.title: Availability
Avl.description: '*' indicates a section not produced in Canada.'+' indicates availability should be checked with supplier.

B.title: Width of flange or horizontal leg

BetX.title: Monosymmetry constant
BetX.description: positive when the larger flange is in flexuralcompression, and negative otherwise, mm. Used for calculating the lateral-torsional buckling moment of monosymmetric beams.(See "Buckling properties of monosymmetric I-beams", Kitipornchai andTrahair, Journal of the Structural Division, ASCE, May 1980)

C.title: Torsion modulus
C.description: ratio of applied torque to maximum shear stress atouter face

Crt.title: Shear constant
Crt.description: ratio of vertical shear force to maximum shear stressfor the strong bending axis

D.title: Depth of section or height of vertical leg

DT.title: Depth-to-thickness ratio of wall or vertical leg

Ix.title: Moment of inertia about axis XX

Iy.title: Moment of inertia about axis YY

K.title: Distance between outer face of flange and web-toe of fillet

K1.title: Distance between middle line of web and flange-toe of fillet

Prp.title: Property group
Prp.description: '*' indicates the first section in a group with similarproperties.

Qf.title: Statical moment at point in flange in line with web face

Qw.title: Statical moment at mid-depth in web

Rop.title: Polar radius of gyration about shear centre

Rx.title: Radius of gyration about axis XX

Rxp.title: Maximum radius of gyration about major principal axis(single angle)

Ry.title: Radius of gyration about axis YY

Ryp.title: Minimum radius of gyration about minor principal axis(single angle)

Ry0.title: Radius of gyration about axis YY (0 mm back-to-back)

Ry8.title: Radius of gyration about axis YY (8 mm back-to-back)

Ry10.title: Radius of gyration about axis YY (10 mm back-to-back)

Ry16.title: Radius of gyration about axis YY (16 mm back-to-back)

Ry20.title: Radius of gyration about axis YY (20 mm back-to-back)

Slp.title: Slope of tapered flange (tangent of angle)

Sx.title: Elastic section modulus about axis XX

Sx2.title: Elastic section modulus about axis XX

TanA.title: Tangent of rotation angle between geometric and principal member axes(single angle)

T1.title: Thickness of tapered flange at tip

T2.title: Thickness of tapered flange at flange-web junction

X.title: Horizontal distance between centroid and outside face of web orvertical leg
